Siemens to Build Manufacturing, Repair Facility in Saudi Arabia

-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 
2011-02-15T13:46:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/siemens-to-build-manufacturing-repair-facility-in-saudi-arabia.html
  Siemens AG  will build a
manufacturing and repair facility in  Saudi Arabia  at a cost of
“hundreds of millions” of U.S. dollars, the company said in an
e-mailed statement today, adding that the facility will include
the local production of gas turbines and rotating equipment.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
